1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Hi! Welcome to Builder Studio — where you build your website in minutes, no code.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:32,000
This is your dashboard — an overview of your sites. Pro features are already on for free for 7 days.

3
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Start with the “Quick start” checklist: four simple steps — create a site, style it, publish, and collect leads.

4
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:22,000
The fastest way is the AI wizard. Describe your business in one sentence and hit “Create”.

5
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:52,000
In the builder you change everything by clicking. There’s also an AI bar: type a command and the site updates itself.

6
00:01:52,000 --> 00:02:12,000
Hit “Publish” and your site is live. We’ll show a QR code right away so you can share it.

7
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:30,000
Leads from your site’s forms land in “Leads”. Under “Team” you invite teammates to work together.

8
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:50,000
When the trial ends, pick a plan on the “Subscription” page. For now, enjoy everything for free.

